       <h1 class="ph">回头是爱 作者/金国栋</h1> 
       <p class="xg1">发布时间：2015-04-08 22:40<span class="pipe">|</span> 有 <script src="/plus/count.php?view=yes&amp;aid=1496&amp;mid=1" type="text/javascript" language="javascript"></script> 位朋友查看</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="s"> 
       <div>
        <strong>独乐乐不如众乐乐，若喜欢，请推荐给您的朋友。我要分享到：</strong>
        <div class="bdsharebuttonbox">
